<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/</link><description>Recent content on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>被人造谣说欠钱不还，朋友圈都传遍了——怎么恢复名誉？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%8D%E8%AA%89%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%8D%E8%AA%89%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>有人在朋友圈、微信群、小区公告栏散布你的不实信息。你的名誉受损了，法律怎么帮你恢复？</description></item><item><title>花了二十万搭的阳光房被城管拆了——违建的钱能找谁赔？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91/</guid><description>买的二手房有个违建阳光房，城管通知要拆。买房的时候前房主没说，中介也没提——损失谁来赔？</description></item><item><title>被限制高消费了，不能坐高铁飞机——怎么解除？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E9%99%90%E9%AB%98%E5%A4%B1%E4%BF%A1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E9%99%90%E9%AB%98%E5%A4%B1%E4%BF%A1/</guid><description>欠了钱被法院判了，没还上，被限高了。飞机高铁坐不了、酒店住不了、孩子上学受影响——怎么才能解除？</description></item><item><title>年底辞职了，年终奖还能拿吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%A5%96/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%A5%96/</guid><description>辛辛苦苦干了一年，年底提了离职，公司说年终奖不发了——这是合法的吗？</description></item><item><title>离了婚就不让我看孩子——法律给我撑腰</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>离婚之后对方不让你看孩子，找了各种理由。你能怎么办？探望权能不能强制执行？</description></item><item><title>兄弟姐妹都不管父母，我一个人撑不住了——赡养义务不是一个人的事</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%B5%A1%E5%85%BB%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%B5%A1%E5%85%BB%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>父母老了需要照顾，兄弟姐妹有的不管、有的少管、有的只管出钱不照顾人。赡养义务怎么分配？</description></item><item><title>朋友拉你入伙做生意，说能赚大钱——当心这不是生意，是传销</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%BC%A0%E9%94%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%BC%A0%E9%94%80/</guid><description>交几千块入会费、拉人头拿提成、层级越多赚得越多——这就是传销。组织者和参与者都有可能构成犯罪。</description></item><item><title>我的照片被商家拿去当广告了——能要多少钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>你的照片被网店拿去当买家秀、被美容院拿去当案例、被培训机构拿去当学员见证——没经过你同意就是侵权。</description></item><item><title>在网上被人造谣了，怎么让对方删帖道歉赔钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B/</guid><description>有人在网上发帖造谣你、曝光你的隐私、煽动别人网暴你。删帖是第一诉求，但后续怎么走法律程序？</description></item><item><title>买了二手房，过户之后发现房子被抵押了——怎么办？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%88%BF%E4%B9%B0%E5%8D%96%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%88%BF%E4%B9%B0%E5%8D%96%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</guid><description>二手房过户之后才发现房子有抵押、有租赁、有户口迁不走。这些隐藏的坑怎么查、怎么避？</description></item><item><title>老公瞒着我给主播打赏了二十万——这钱能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E6%89%93%E8%B5%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E6%89%93%E8%B5%8F/</guid><description>配偶偷偷给主播打赏了几十万，属于擅自处分夫妻共同财产。能不能要求主播和平台返还？</description></item><item><title>楼上每天晚上十一点开始蹦迪——噪音扰民怎么治？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%99%AA%E9%9F%B3%E6%89%B0%E6%B0%91/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%99%AA%E9%9F%B3%E6%89%B0%E6%B0%91/</guid><description>楼上邻居天天半夜闹腾，沟通没用，物业不管，警察来了走了之后又吵。走法律途径能怎么解决？</description></item><item><title>快递丢了，快递公司说只赔三倍运费——合法吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%92%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%92%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1/</guid><description>寄了一个包裹值两千块，快递丢了。快递公司说你没保价，只赔三倍运费也就是三十块。合理吗？</description></item><item><title>物业服务太差了，能不能不交物业费？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</guid><description>物业只收钱不干事——垃圾没人清、电梯老坏、门禁是摆设。业主可以不交物业费吗？</description></item><item><title>试用期被辞退，有赔偿吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%AF%95%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%AF%95%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/</guid><description>试用期不是白用期。公司不能在试用期随便让你走人，不能延长试用期，不能不给工资。</description></item><item><title>网恋对象带我投资，一个月赚了三十万——这三十万是假的，我投进去的二十万是真的</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%9D%80%E7%8C%AA%E7%9B%98/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%9D%80%E7%8C%AA%E7%9B%98/</guid><description>杀猪盘——先跟你谈恋爱，再带你投资，最后卷走你全部积蓄。这种骗局怎么识别？被骗了怎么办？</description></item><item><title>签了合同付了款，对方根本没打算履行——这是合同纠纷还是合同诈骗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97/</guid><description>合同纠纷和合同诈骗的界限在哪？什么情况下民事纠纷能升级成刑事案件？</description></item><item><title>被电信诈骗骗了钱，报警之后钱能追回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97/</guid><description>电信诈骗被骗了几万块，报警了，多久能破案？钱能不能追回来？追回来能拿回多少？</description></item><item><title>万顺叫车，很多人被骗了——网约车加盟骗局的套路</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%B8%87%E9%A1%BA%E5%8F%AB%E8%BD%A6%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%B8%87%E9%A1%BA%E5%8F%AB%E8%BD%A6%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</guid><description>交几千块加盟费就能跑网约车、月入过万？万顺叫车让无数司机血本无归。这种加盟模式的法律问题在哪？</description></item><item><title>花三万块请人代运营拼多多店铺，一个月卖了三单——钱能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8B%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8B%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</guid><description>代运营公司承诺月销过万，收了钱之后店铺根本没流量。这是服务纠纷还是诈骗？怎么把钱要回来？</description></item><item><title>离了婚，孩子跟我，对方该给多少抚养费？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%8A%9A%E5%85%BB%E8%B4%B9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%8A%9A%E5%85%BB%E8%B4%B9/</guid><description>抚养费该给多少、给到什么时候、不给怎么办——离婚后最容易被拖欠的不是感情，是养孩子的钱。</description></item><item><title>投了钱给高息理财，老板跑路了——你的钱还能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84/</guid><description>年化收益率百分之二十、保本保息、介绍朋友还有佣金——这不是理财，这是非法集资。钱被卷走了怎么办？</description></item><item><title>喝了一杯啤酒开车，被抓了——后果比你想象的严重</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%85%92%E9%A9%BE%E9%86%89%E9%A9%BE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%85%92%E9%A9%BE%E9%86%89%E9%A9%BE/</guid><description>酒驾和醉驾的界限在哪里？酒驾是违法，醉驾是犯罪。那一杯啤酒，可能就是犯罪记录的分水岭。</description></item><item><title>你的个人信息被卖了，能告谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2/</guid><description>刚买了房，装修公司电话就来了。刚生了孩子，早教机构就来推销。谁卖了你的信息？你能索赔多少？</description></item><item><title>老公在外面欠的钱，老婆要还吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%80%BA%E5%8A%A1/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%80%BA%E5%8A%A1/</guid><description>配偶在外面借的钱、担保的债、投资亏的钱——离婚的时候这些债你要不要一起背？民法典说得很清楚。</description></item><item><title>离职之后公司不让你去同行上班——竞业限制你该拿多少钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E7%AB%9E%E4%B8%9A%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E7%AB%9E%E4%B8%9A%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>签了竞业限制协议，离职后两年内不能去同行。但公司每个月要给你补偿金。不给钱？协议自动作废。</description></item><item><title>你家狗咬了人，赔多少？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E5%92%AC%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E5%92%AC%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>遛狗没拴绳，咬了路人。医药费、误工费、精神损害抚慰金——狗主人要赔哪些？如果被咬的人先招惹了狗呢？</description></item><item><title>天上掉下来一个花盆，砸到人了——整栋楼都要赔？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%9B%E7%89%A9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%9B%E7%89%A9/</guid><description>高空抛物砸到人，找不到是谁扔的。整栋楼的住户都要赔吗？物业有责任吗？民法典说了什么？</description></item><item><title>网购的东西不想要了，商家说拆了包装不给退——合法吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</guid><description>网购的东西拆了包装还能退吗？哪些商品不适用七天无理由？商家拒退怎么办？</description></item><item><title>加班费到底怎么算？很多人被公司忽悠了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B4%B9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B4%B9/</guid><description>工作日加班1.5倍、休息日2倍、法定节假日3倍。你的加班费拿对了吗？</description></item><item><title>上班路上摔了一跤，算不算工伤？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BC%A4%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BC%A4%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A/</guid><description>在上班路上被车撞了算工伤吗？在公司团建时受伤呢？在家加班猝死呢？工伤认定的边界比你想象的宽。</description></item><item><title>你用了好几年的店名，被别人抢注了商标——还能继续用吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%95%86%E6%A0%87%E6%8A%A2%E6%B3%A8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%95%86%E6%A0%87%E6%8A%A2%E6%B3%A8/</guid><description>小店开了五年，生意刚有起色，突然收到律师函说你侵犯了别人的商标权。这个你用了五年的名字，现在不属于你了？</description></item><item><title>和朋友合伙做生意，没签协议——散伙的时候怎么算账</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%90%88%E4%BC%99%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%90%88%E4%BC%99%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</guid><description>跟朋友合伙开餐厅，一人出钱一人出力，没签协议。两年后要散伙，投进去的二十万怎么拿回来？</description></item><item><title>被人打了，除了报警还能做什么？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86/</guid><description>被打了，很多人只知道报警。但报警只是第一步。如何验伤、如何索赔、是治安案件还是刑事案件——这些你都得知道。</description></item><item><title>拆迁补偿不合理，你能做什么？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E6%8B%86%E8%BF%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E6%8B%86%E8%BF%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF/</guid><description>拆迁办给的补偿方案远低于市场价，不签字就断水断电。征收补偿不合理，法律给你的反击武器比你想象的多。</description></item><item><title>医院出了事，怎么证明是医院的错？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E7%BA%A0%E7%BA%B7/</guid><description>做手术出了并发症，是正常风险还是医疗事故？发生了医疗纠纷该怎么取证、找谁鉴定、索赔多少？</description></item><item><title>买了保险出了事，保险公司说这不赔那不赔——怎么让他赔</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8B%92%E8%B5%94/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8B%92%E8%B5%94/</guid><description>买了保险，出了事找保险公司理赔，对方翻出合同里的一条免责条款说这事不在理赔范围——怎么办？</description></item><item><title>网上搜了张图片用在公众号上，结果被告了——赔了三万</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%BE%B5%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%BE%B5%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>百度搜张图、微博扒张图、别人公众号的图直接拿来用——你觉得自己只是顺手，但法律上这叫侵权。</description></item><item><title>装修装了三分之一，老板跑了——剩下的钱和烂摊子怎么办</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%AF/</guid><description>装修公司收了钱跑路了，家里水电没做完、地砖铺了一半、墙上到处是坑。已经付的十几万装修款怎么追？</description></item><item><title>公司欠钱不还，能让老板个人还吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%9C%E8%BF%9E%E5%B8%A6%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%9C%E8%BF%9E%E5%B8%A6%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB/</guid><description>公司欠你钱，公司账户上没钱，老板开着豪车住着别墅。能让老板个人还吗？</description></item><item><title>口头协议算不算数？说好的事情对方不认了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%B4%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%B4%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</guid><description>没签书面合同，就只有一句口头承诺。对方反悔了，你能怎么办？口头协议有没有法律效力？</description></item><item><title>婚没结成，彩礼能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%BD%A9%E7%A4%BC%E8%BF%94%E8%BF%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%BD%A9%E7%A4%BC%E8%BF%94%E8%BF%98/</guid><description>谈了两年，彩礼给了，婚期定了，临门一脚分手了。十八万八的彩礼——能要回来多少？</description></item><item><title>遗产怎么继承？没有遗嘱的情况下，钱和房子归谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF/</guid><description>人走了，没有留遗嘱。配偶、孩子、父母——谁先拿、谁后拿、谁拿多少。法律早就排好了顺序。</description></item><item><title>买了房，定金付了，房东反悔不卖了——他能说不卖就不卖？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%B9%B0%E6%88%BF%E5%AE%9A%E9%87%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%B9%B0%E6%88%BF%E5%AE%9A%E9%87%91/</guid><description>你看中一套房子，签了合同付了定金，房东突然说有人出价更高不卖了。定金退你还是双倍退你？</description></item><item><title>帮人转了一笔账，结果成了犯罪——帮信罪离你有多近</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%B8%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BD%AA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%B8%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BD%AA/</guid><description>朋友让你帮忙转一笔钱，或者借你的银行卡用一下——你可能正在犯帮信罪。这个罪名近年来起诉人数已经冲到前三了。</description></item><item><title>买到了假货，除了退货还能让他赔你三倍</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</guid><description>买到假货别光退货。法律规定经营者欺诈的退一赔三，最低赔五百。很多人不知道这条，白白吃亏。</description></item><item><title>出了交通事故，对方全责但不赔钱，你拿他一点办法都没有？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E7%90%86%E8%B5%94/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E7%90%86%E8%B5%94/</guid><description>被撞了，对方全责，但他就是不赔钱。没有保险？司机跑了？这些情况下你的钱谁来赔？</description></item><item><title>楼上漏水把你家淹了，对方不赔怎么办？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4/</guid><description>楼上漏水泡了你家天花板，对方说不是他的责任。物业、开发商、楼上邻居——到底该找谁？</description></item><item><title>公司让你走人，一分钱不赔？这三笔钱你该拿</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BE%9E%E9%80%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BE%9E%E9%80%80/</guid><description>被辞退的时候，公司该赔你多少钱？经济补偿金、赔偿金、代通知金——三笔钱，很多人一笔都没拿到。</description></item><item><title>离婚的时候，房子到底归谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A6%BB%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A6%BB%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</guid><description>婚前买房、婚后还贷、父母出资——离婚时房子怎么分，比你想象的复杂得多。</description></item><item><title>借条怎么写才有效？少写一个字，钱可能就要不回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</guid><description>借条和欠条一字之差，法律后果天差地别。借钱出去之前花三分钟看完这篇，省掉将来三年的麻烦。</description></item><item><title>公司不跟你签劳动合同？别慌，你赚了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%80%8D%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%80%8D%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84/</guid><description>很多人以为不签劳动合同是公司占便宜。错了，是公司给你送钱——法律规定超过一个月不签合同，每月赔你双倍工资，最多赔11个月。</description></item><item><title>租房押金被扣了？房东敢扣你钱，你就敢让他吐出来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</guid><description>退房的时候房东找各种理由扣你押金——墙壁脏了、家电旧了、地板花了。哪些该你赔，哪些不该？律师说清楚。</description></item><item><title>别人欠你钱不还？不用打官司也能把钱要回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</guid><description>欠钱不还，一定要打官司吗？律师告诉你一条更快的路——支付令。15天出结果，费用只要诉讼的十分之一。</description></item><item><title>朋友借钱你担保？一个签名，一套房子没了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</guid><description>帮朋友在借条上签了个名，结果被执行了一套房子。担保这件事，99%的人都没当回事——等出事的时候，已经晚了。</description></item><item><title>关于曹义德律师</title><link>https://caoyide.com/about/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 20:23:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/about/</guid><description/></item><item><title>关于曹义德律师</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/clippings/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%9B%B9%E4%B9%89%E5%BE%B7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/clippings/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%9B%B9%E4%B9%89%E5%BE%B7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88/</guid><description># 执业背景
曹义德律师，湖北江通律师事务所执业律师
